# Privacy Policy — Baby Inventory

**Last updated:** January 22, 2026

BabyDaily ("the App") is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy describes how we handle information when you use the App.

---

## 1. Data We Do Not Collect

The App **does not collect, transmit, or store** any personal data about you or your child. We do not use:

- Analytics or usage tracking  
- Advertising identifiers or ad tracking  
- Crash reporting that sends data off your device  
- Any third-party analytics, marketing, or tracking SDKs  

Your use of the App is not monitored or recorded by us.

---

## 2. Where Your Data Lives

**All data stays on your device.**

- Baby profiles, milestones, and any information you enter are stored **only on your iPhone or iPad**.
- We do not upload, sync, or back up your data to our servers or any cloud service.
- We have no access to your data. If you delete the App, that data is removed with it.

---

## 3. In-App Purchases

The App may offer in-app purchases (e.g. "Full Access" and other products).

- **Payment processing** is handled entirely by **Apple**. We do not see or store your payment method, card number, or billing details.
- Apple may collect and process data related to your purchase in accordance with [Apple’s Privacy Policy](https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/).
- Purchase state (e.g. whether you have unlocked Full Access) is stored **only on your device** so the App can show the correct content. We do not receive or store this information on our side.

---

## 4. Third-Party Services

The App does not integrate third-party services that collect your data. We do not use social login, analytics, or advertising networks.

---

## 5. Your Rights and Choices

- **Access and control:** All data the App uses is on your device. You can view, edit, or delete it within the App (e.g. edit or delete baby profiles).
- **Deletion:** Uninstalling the App removes all of its data from your device.
- **No account:** The App does not require an account. There is no central service that holds your information.

If you have questions about this policy or the App, you can contact us at the support URL provided in the App Store listing.

---

## 6. Changes to This Policy

We may update this privacy policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top will be revised when we do. Continued use of the App after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.

---

## 7. Contact

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, You can contact us:

By email: hajiangwork@gmail.com
